0.1.name: wordpress/mootools-collapsing-archives
0.1.description:
This is a relatively simple plugin that uses Javascript based on MooTools framework to make the Archive links in the sidebar collapsable by year and/or month. Fork of Rob Felty's Collapsing Archives.

Multiple languages content is now fully supported through compatibility with qTranslate and WPML Multilingual CMS

Plugin Homepage

http://www.3dolab.net/en/mootools-collapsing-categories-and-archives

What's new?

See the CHANGELOG for more information
